  <entry>
    <id>https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/releases/tag/v1.3.0</id>
    <title>New release for Pingvin Share: v1.3.0</title>
    <updated>2024-11-14T13:10:59-05:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>stonith404/pingvin-share</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;h3&gt;Features&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;add 'secureCookies' configuration variable to explicitly set the secure flag and prevent confusion (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/4ce64206be7440a99299e1ed238ced7408c0563d"&gt;4ce6420&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;add confirm dialog for leaving the page if an upload is in progress (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/d8084e401d7572b2d6e38ffa20cb678a0fb0e615"&gt;d8084e4&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Bug Fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;improve share completed dialog redirection for reverse shares (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/4ef7ebb0622f16d2d2c4d114b5fc15298e2ba24f"&gt;4ef7ebb&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;prevent deletion of last admin account (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/e1a5d195448e3d741b77fb982ce515489a360562"&gt;e1a5d19&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;throw error if no disk space is left (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/c26de4e881edfe6c7db617c0aeba89871397ebe2"&gt;c26de4e&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;use current window url instead of app url in frontend (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/6f45c3b1fbf4a95b29e5742878b55a1afa0b8886"&gt;6f45c3b&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Sponsors&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thank you @jwdoll and @wlburks for your tips. I really appreciate it ❤️&lt;/p&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/releases/tag/v1.3.0" rel="alternate"/>
  </entry>
