&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;remote arbitrary file overwrite on file upload endpoint (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pingvin-share/commit/6cf5c66fe2eda1e0a525edf7440d047fe2f0e35b"&gt;6cf5c66&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
